lead_paragraph: Markieff Morris overcame a rude welcome in his Phoenix return by scoring 21 points and helping the Washington Wizards beat the Suns 106-99 Friday night in a much-needed victory for their playoff hopes.

headline.print_headline: Morris Shines in Return to Phoenix, Wizards Dump Suns 106-99
